*.apk
*.aab
*.keystore
# Shared debug keystore is public-by-design (per IMPL-02) so the SHA-1 is stable across
# developers and CI; release keystores still match the rule above.
!debug.keystore
google-services.json
# The phone app's google-services.json holds only public Firebase identifiers
# (project number, app ID, package, restrictable API key) and is required by the
# google-services Gradle plugin at build time (IMPL-AND-20, FCM). Safe to commit;
# the sensitive backend Firebase Admin credential never lives in the repo.
!app/google-services.json
